             String director,
             ArrayList<String> cast,
             String releaseDate,
             String endDate,
             String synopsis,
             int duration,
             showingStatus_Enum showingStatus,
             movieType_Enum movieType,
             movieRating_Enum movieRating,
             int ticketSales)
        Constructor
        Parameters:
        title - Movie title
        director - Movie director
        cast - Movie cast (at least 2)
        releaseDate - Movie release date
        endDate - Movie ending date
        synopsis - Movie synopsis
        duration - Movie runtime
        showingStatus - Movie showing status (Now showing, Coming soon or Preview)
        movieType - Movie type (2D, 3D or Blockbuster)
        movieRating - Movie rating (PG, PG13, NC16, M18 or R21)
        ticketSales - Movie ticket sales
